channel.title: Line 10: [Error] (14837:1): Duplicate identifier '' in script
channel.description:
I've been working on my Al-Kharid warrior killer , and i keep getting this error when compiling :mad: Line 10: [Error] (14837:1): Duplicate identifier '' in script on line ten there is this
fmode=2;//fightmode you wish to use
It keeps saying that there's an error in the 1 space on that line , and there's nothing there , i changing the layout of my script but still nothing . :confused: :confused: Anyone want to elaborate on this for me a little please ? Thanks ~ hai

item.title: Line 10: [Error] (14837:1): Duplicate identifier '' in script
item.dc:creator: @Cheesehunk Cheesehunk
item.description:
@Cheesehunk wrote:

thiefmn6092:

It’s my job, Your welcome

Who hired you? :eek:

Also, remember to assign a variable something you need :=, to ask if a variable equals something use =.

Example.

Procedure Example; var numb : integer; begin numb:=Random(5); //:= Declares numb to a number between 0, and 4. if (numb>3) then writeln('Number was greater than 3.');//> is the greater than sign, when comparing two integers; if (numb<3) then writeln('Number was less than 3.');//< is the less than sign, when comparing two integers; if (numb=3) then writeln('Number was 3.');//= checks if the integers are the same. end;
